               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>Loose pages, most likely from a scrapbook, including photographs with handwritten text and illustrations by David Piel, recounting the arrival of the First Marine Division, Radio Team, in Peiping, China; the signing of the surrender of North China; views of the Summer Palace; V-J Day; Special Service bulletins listing social events for soldiers; and related memorabilia.</p>
